1634  [return: NotNull]
1635  internal static int Utf8Size([NotNull] string str) => str.Validate().Length * 4 + 1;
1636 
1644  [return: NotNull]
1645  internal static byte[] Utf8Encode([NotNull]string str, [NotNull] byte[] buffer, [NotNull] int bufferSize)
1646  {
1647  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str.Validate(), 0, str.Validate().Length, buffer, 0);
1648  buffer[str.Length] = 0;
1649  return buffer;
1650  }
1651 
1657  internal static byte[] Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
1658  {
1659  if (str == null)
1660  {
1661  return null;
1662  }
1663 
1664  int bufferSize = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(str) + 1;
1665  byte[] buffer = new byte[bufferSize];
1666  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
1667  buffer[bufferSize - 1] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
1668 
1669  return buffer;
1670  }
1671 
1672 
1679  public static string Utf8ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
1680  {
1681  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
1682  {
1683  return null;
1684  }
1685 
1686  int len = 0;
1687  while (Marshal.ReadByte(s, len) != 0)
1688  {
1689  len++;
1690  }
1691 
1692  if (len == 0)
1693  {
1694  return string.Empty;
1695  }
1696 
1697  byte[] bytes = new byte[len];
1698  Marshal.Copy(s, bytes, 0, len);
1699  string result = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(bytes);
1700 
1701  if (freePtr)
1702  {
1703  SDL_free(s);
1704  }
1705 
1706  return result;
1707  }

1718  private static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

2667  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2668  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId);
2669 
2670 
2676  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2677  {
2678  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2679  {
2680  return IntPtr.Zero;
2681  }
2682 
2683  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2684  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
2685  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2686  return mem;
2687  }
2688 
2695  public static int SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId)
2696  {
2697  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2698  {
2699  flags = messageBoxData.flags,
2700  window = messageBoxData.window,
2701  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.title),
2702  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.message),
2703  numbuttons = messageBoxData.numbuttons
2704  };
2705 
2706  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageBoxData.numbuttons];
2707  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2708 
2709  try
2710  {
2711  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2712  {
2713  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2714  {
2715  flags = messageBoxData.buttons[i].flags,
2716  buttonId = messageBoxData.buttons[i].buttonId,
2717  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.buttons[i].text)
2718  };
2719  }
2720 
2721  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2722  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2723  {
2724  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
2725  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2726  }
2727 
2728  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2729 
2730  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2731  if (messageBoxData.colorScheme != null)
2732  {
2733  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2734  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageBoxData.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2735  }
2736 
2737  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonId);
2738 
2739  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2740  {
2741  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2742  }
2743 
2744  SDL_free(data.message);
2745  SDL_free(data.title);
2746 
2747  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2748  {
2749  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2750  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2751  }
2752 
2753  return result;
2754  }
2755  finally
2756  {
2757  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2758  {
2759  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2760  }
2761  }
2762  }
2763

5977  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFourcc(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);
5978 
5988  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFormat(
5989  SdlPixelType type,
5990  uint order,
5991  SdlPackedLayout layout,
5992  byte bits,
5993  byte bytes
5994  )
5995  => (uint) (
5996  (1 << 28) |
5997  ((byte) type << 24) |
5998  ((byte) order << 20) |
5999  ((byte) layout << 16) |
6000  (bits << 8) |
6001  bytes
6002  );
6003 
6009  private static byte SdlPixelFlag(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
6010 
6016  private static byte SdlPixelType(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
6017 
6023  private static byte SdlPixelOrder(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
6024 
6030  public static byte SdlPixelLayout(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6031 
6037  public static byte SdlBitsPerPixel(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
6038 
6044  public static byte SdlBytesPerPixel(uint x)
6045  {
6046  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(x))
6047  {
6048  if (x == SdlPixelFormatYuy2 ||
6049  x == SdlPixelFormatUy ||
6050  x == SdlPixelFormatYv)
6051  {
6052  return 2;
6053  }
6054 
6055  return 1;
6056  }
6057 
6058  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6059  }
6060 
6066  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatIndexed(uint format)
6067  {
6068  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6069  {
6070  return false;
6071  }
6072 
6073  SdlPixelType pType =
6074  (SdlPixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6075  return pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6076  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6077  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6078  }
6079 
6085  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(uint format)
6086  {
6087  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6088  {
6089  return false;
6090  }
6091 
6092  SdlPixelType pType =
6093  (SdlPixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6094  return pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6095  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6096  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6097  }
6098 
6104  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatArray(uint format)
6105  {
6106  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6107  {
6108  return false;
6109  }
6110 
6111  SdlPixelType pType =
6112  (SdlPixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6113  return pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6114  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6115  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6116  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6117  pType == Enums.SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6118  }
6119 
6125  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatAlpha(uint format)
6126  {
6127  if (SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(format))
6128  {
6129  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6130  (SdlPackedOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
6131  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6132  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6133  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6134  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6135  }
6136 
6137  if (SdlIsPixelFormatArray(format))
6138  {
6139  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6140  (SdlArrayOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
6141  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6142  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6143  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6144  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6145  }
6146 
6147  return false;
6148  }
6149 
6155  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatFour(uint format) => (format == 0) && (SdlPixelFlag(format) != 1);

7390  public static SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7391  out SdlEventFilter filter,
7392  out IntPtr userdata
7393  )
7394  {
7395  SdlBool val = SDL_GetEventFilter(out IntPtr result, out userdata);
7396  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
7397  {
7398  filter = (SdlEventFilter) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
7399  result,
7400  typeof(SdlEventFilter)
7401  );
7402  }
7403  else
7404  {
7405  filter = null;
7406  }
7407 
7408  return val;
7409  }

8855  public static SdlGameControllerButtonBind SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
8856  IntPtr gameController,
8857  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
8858  )

8862  gameController,
8863  axis
8864  );

8866  {

8868  };
8869  result.value.hat.hat = dumb.unionVal0;
8870  result.value.hat.hat_mask = dumb.unionVal1;
8871  return result;
